project_descr: Procurement of medicines for treatment of Hep C

outputs.output_descr: Provision of support for capacity development of “SK-Pharmacy”, LLP in the field of procurement of medicines, health products and medical equipment to contribute to early detection of Hep C and other socially significant diseases, to enable equal access of Kazakhstani people to timely and prompt treatment and thus promoting decrease of the rate of socially significant diseases prevalence in the Republic of Kazakhstan.

project_title: procurement of medicines for treatment of hep c
